  <brief_title>Evaluation of Safety of ZyComb® In Patients With Common Cold - ZIP 3000 (XY-005-IM)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Non-interventional, Non-controlled, Post-marketing Study to Obtain Knowledge of the Safety of ZyComb® (Xylometazoline Hydrochloride 0.5 mg/mL and Ipratropium Bromide 0.6 mg/mL) for Symptoms of Common Cold in a Real-life OTC Setting</official_title>
  <sponsors>
