  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objectives of the study are to obtain knowledge about the safety in use, the patients'
      general impression of the treatment and the pattern of use of ZyComb® in an over-the-counter
      (OTC) setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
